<C>__{bucky}
<D>__{german.}
<C>__{emmett sprague}
<D>__{a great people, the germans. hitler was a bit excessive, but mark my words that someday we'll regret not joining forces with him to fight the reds. i killed a lot of your countrymen during the war.}
