<D>__{an old friend stuffed him. we were in the scots regiment together. georgie tilden. he wanted to work in the flickers.}
<C>__{bucky}
<D>__{so when did you come here?}
<C>__{emmett sprague}
<D>__{1920. hollywood was a cow pasture, but the silent flickers was booming. georgie got work as a lighting man, and me building houses. georgie got me introduced to mack sennett and i helped him build that housing project he was putting up hollywoodland underneath that godawful sign.}
<C>__{bucky}
<D>__{i always loved the keystone kops.}
<C>__{emmett sprague}
<D>__{old mack knew how to squeeze a dollar dry, he did. he had extras moonlighting as laborers and vice versa. i used to drive 'em over to hollywoodland after twelve hours on a keystone cops flicker and put in another six hours by torchlight. even gave me as assistant director credit a couple times, so grateful he was for the way i squeezed his slaves }
<A>__{a screech interrupts emmett's monologue. bucky looks across the table to see ramona trying to corral a potato with her fork (the source of the sound).}
